ReadMe

Class Name: PlaylistManagerMain

Difficulty: Level 3 — Interactive Object-Oriented Application

Estimated Time: 80–110 minutes

Actual Time Taken: 87 minutes

Written by: Chanwoo Park

Problem
Create an interactive playlist manager that allows users to add,
view, search, and remove songs, view a summary, and save the
summary to a text file.

Program Flow
Create a Scanner and Playlist, repeatedly display the menu,
process the selected action, and stop when the user selects Exit.

Class Responsibilities
PlaylistManagerMain handles input and menu flow.
Playlist manages songs and summary calculations.
Song represents one song.
MusicGenre defines allowed genres.
PlaylistFileWriter writes summary text to a file.